data.description:
5 Bed, 3 bath home with over 2000 sqft near downtown Cuero! This 2014 home with a split floor plan is on almost half an acre in the desired town of Cuero. The roof and water heater are 2 1/2 years old. This mobile home is fully tape and textured with AC vents in the ceiling. Enjoy the large garden tub in the Primary bathroom. Two of the guest bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom. One of the extra bedrooms is currently used as an office. 

There is a brand new, metal covered back patio that leads to the above ground pool. Spend your evenings relaxing out back after a hard day of work. There is also a storage building in the large, privacy-fenced back yard. There is a gravel semi-circle driveway for plenty of parking.

Schedule your showings today!
